Sentence: They include genes encoding three subunits of the cytochrome oxidase ( cox1 to 3), apocytochrome b ( cob), seven subunits of the NADH dehydrogenase complex ( nad1 to 6, nad4L), two ATPase subunits ( atp6 and atp9), three ribosomal RNAs ( rrn5, srn and lrn), 23 tRNAs and four ribosomal proteins ( rps3, rps11, rps12 and rpl16).
